Text:
As usual thank you.............

Just off to bed to watch last weeks on my PSP (sad I know........)

Thanks for your work in sharing the entire season of this great show!

Now that season 1 is finished I'm going to have to wait for Feast and Wrong Turn 2 to get my Rollins fix.  Terrible......just terrible.
Thanks for posting this and the other Rollins shows, your efforts are really appreciated. We don't get the HR show in the UK.
Thanks, and let's keep HR up, youth today needs to watch shows like this.
